706152f-a.title: Brooklyn: Shore Road - 68th Street
706152f-a.text:
Owls Head Park: A set of 3 views from different angles of the Bliss
Mansion therein; No. 1 being from Shore Road (western boundary), north of
68th Street.
April 29, 1929.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
